                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>[[/r 2d8 + 18 # bludgeoning damage]]{2d8 + 18 bludgeoning damage}, <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Constrict DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"39\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic fortitude</span> save</p>\n<p>The monster deals the listed amount of damage to any number of creatures @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Grabbed]{Grabbed} or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Restrained]{Restrained} by it. Each of those creatures can attempt a basic Fortitude save with the listed DC.</p>"
